0Z","msg":"樓主逃避完未 面對現實啦"},{"pid":"82d584b3ef43b9c6c1cdd5a935db262b820fe75d","tid":2129691,"uid":332538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T00:13:31.000Z","msg":"同意<br />\n我每個月都收緊租<br />\n睇下個租客有無過數落我戶口<br />\n每月都重覆<br />\n墮入輪迴地獄<br />\n好多苦難<br />\n<br />\n窮人應該都有下一代嘅權利<br />\n我亦都好鼓勵佢地生育<br />\n佢地唔生<br />\n邊有人租樓<br />\n我個仔讀國際學校<br />\n去外國讀書<br />\n返到來香港都要搵啲人襯托下"},{"pid":"a8da6ae658417d5615399c2e7f4ffb56471498a1","tid":2129691,"uid":26329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"de43e80cdad8b4cfbaa1c258fad538bd18b0512c","tid":2129691,"uid":5574,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"681da0af15f66eb6f0f5b756cc692bad229af908","tid":2129691,"uid":105678,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"e86ccdda45dde648d9f029e8fa1c6ba26421247c","tid":2129691,"uid":5574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T19:09:57.000Z","msg":"呢樣咪係佛學遠離真相囉..<br />\n人生係無目的都講得出"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T19:13:32.000Z","msg":"師兄newage？"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T19:15:04.000Z","msg":"我 newage or not 有關系 ?<br />\n同埋點解我一定係師兄 ?<br />\n你覺唔覺得你太主觀 ?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T00:28:33.000Z","msg":"人生有咩目的?只係自己想要有目的而創造一個目的"},{"pid":"d7f54653b6aa2b2c4395559860c5079f0d920c14","tid":2129691,"uid":54305,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a3ac2e4e338064ba98297b2a8f94a7be14f9014f","tid":2129691,"uid":105678,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"b6e6ac8cebe5f13bc3ada6483d961b22796af89f","tid":2129691,"uid":5574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5734fce3c72f2bb1ccef7e216902c31326425acc","tid":2129691,"uid":105678,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T19:05:20.000Z","msg":"苦海無涯，回頭是岸"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T19:07:03.000Z","msg":"如果你覺得人嘅一生係之前設定好嘅<br />\n咁苦難都係今世嘅功課<br />\n叫人遠離亦都只會浪費一次人生"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T19:08:55.000Z","msg":"人生唔係功課，本身係無目的，而業力導致因果不斷輪迴不止，唯有受果而不造因先係唯一解脫"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T01:03